Package repository

Class DoctorRepository

java.lang.Object
repository.DoctorRepository
All Implemented Interfaces:
IDoctorRepository, IRepository<Doctor>
public class DoctorRepository extends Object implements IDoctorRepository
An implementation of IDoctorRepository that operates on Doctor data models. It extends the functionality of a UserRepository through dependency injection to focus on Users that are specifically Doctors.
Since:
2024-11-17
